reviewText: I loved everything about the movie, couldn't stop watching, didn't want it to end.  Hooked!
My husband loves the Dexter series thank you

I can watch Dexter over and over,...so it's nice to have a DVD with some of the best episodes in one place. The extra interviews are ok ( I believe they can be found on youtube) but for 14.99 it's worth it for any Dexter fan!
Even though I saw these episodes before, I really liked it
